Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.57,0:02:11.65,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}こそばゆいけど耳かして　囁いた本気だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:18.75,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ナゾカケーホラーエンジン発進　いま決めたアイになれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:26.02,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}とまらないよね　でも最高　鳴り響く勝利のベル
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:33.51,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}平和にさえ勇気ひつよう　目指すのは未知の空路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:40.55,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}調子イイね拍子抜け　答えが残念だって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:50.16,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大スキになっちゃうよ　悔しくココロ騒いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:55.06,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}憧れのMOON LIGHT　遠くて茫然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:58.83,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}シアワセだって窓越える
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.85,0:03:02.14,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}HIGH LIGHT　どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:06.23,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}落ち着かない恋の果て
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:16.11,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}試練は可憐にパスして　もうだいじょうぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.57,0:02:11.65,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}雖然有點癢  但還是把耳朵湊近點  輕聲嘟嚷自己是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:18.75,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}猜謎  鬧鬼  引擎發動  化為剛定下來的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:26.02,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}已經無法阻止  但這種感覺很棒不是嗎  勝利之鐘聲響徹長空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:33.51,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}太平世界仍需勇氣  目標是未知的航空路線
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:40.55,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}狀態很好  真沒想到  得到的回覆令人遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:50.16,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}變得更加喜歡了  心臟就如小鹿亂漲  有點不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:55.06,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}憧憬的MOON LIGHT  既遙遠又模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:58.83,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}幸福也能透過窗戶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.85,0:03:02.14,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}HIGH LIGHT  直到天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:06.23,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無法平靜的戀情  直到永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:16.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}華麗地通過試煉  已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.38,0:22:08.45,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8}You always wish upon stars
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.18,0:22:12.15,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8}I don't know what you long for
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.71,0:22:18.88,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8}Because everything that I need is here by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:23.04,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8}We named some stars out of reach
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:26.67,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8}Listened to the wind sung
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.33,0:22:30.00,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}We are little kids but
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.00,0:22:33.52,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}We know what is worth for us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.43,0:22:38.31,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Someday you'll find that what you've been longing for is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.31,0:22:41.85,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Here in this small town you don't like
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.85,0:22:49.00,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Someday I say the words I've never said to anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:52.59,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}You make me smile，make me cry，
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.59,0:22:56.26,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Make me feel that I can fly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.26,0:23:02.69,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Sure you belong to me like I belong to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:03.37,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I said，
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.55,0:23:09.50,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}"I'm on your side even when you are wrong"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.50,0:23:13.35,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I wanna be your hero to save you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.35,0:23:21.51,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}From everything that hurt you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.30,0:00:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始移植核心  你有什麼話要我轉告給米利安姆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.59,0:00:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  那個…這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米利安姆大概會生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.59,0:00:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.03,0:00:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這不算是為了米利安姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.36,0:00:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我想這麼做才這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是為了米利安姆小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.56,0:00:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是因為我想把我的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把魂白珠送給米利安姆所以才給她的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.84,0:01:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這些嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.79,0:01:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我要說的就這些
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.34,0:01:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓她變成健康的米利安姆哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.75,0:01:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.02,0:01:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.88,0:01:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  被叫姐姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.38,0:01:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米利安姆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.04,0:01:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:29.20,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,270)\fad(1000,0)}各自的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:29.20,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,270)\fad(1000,0)}各自的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米內特  你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉娜  米內特她！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大家也都在找她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔跟我從天上找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙緹  你明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力搜查開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜查完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在森林地區查到疑似米內特小姐的魂白珠的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全速趕往那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.63,0:04:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全速啟動  瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請好好抓緊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好幹哦  雷斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有強力的艾爾反應接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙緹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你們過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙緹  把雷斯塔送到有反應的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.71,0:05:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來都是依賴著雷斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這次就由我來讓你依賴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法發動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝您武運昌盛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.71,0:05:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不讓你過去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就由我來拖住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑得快的對手就用數量來對付
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雕蟲小技
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都讓她躲過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.93,0:06:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現強大的聖者遺物的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得太美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對象無傷  攻擊被無效化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像個貓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武技強大  還有戰鬥用的聖者遺物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為勝利幾率非常低
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很強  不能就這麼放過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明得快點趕回去…立刻了結她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的被她預料到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,條件反射  剛才是以她的直覺來迴避的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太難纏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你挺強的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如你有想要保護的人  我一樣有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  所以我不會留手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然來了嗎  雷斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.79,0:08:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿貝丁…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把米內特還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿貝丁  如果我站在你的立場上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許會跟你選擇同一條路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.91,0:08:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是要是你站在現在的我的立場上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定會像我一樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們的路就不會相容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就要讓它們相容的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚臍要給搶走的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了莉特絲  表情那麼嚴肅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:09:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  只是想起只有姐姐的衣服還晾在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的也收回去啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.72,0:09:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濕溜溜的姐姐不是很性感嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想洗過的衣服還濕溜溜的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這種事  還是快趕路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得趕緊把那件事告訴大家才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.18,0:09:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要拯救米利安姆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.29,0:09:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想妨礙的話  我就不會放過你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥用聖者遺物？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我和阿薇莉爾為了戰鬥而在體內裝了好幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.88,0:10:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  你沒事啊米內特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  為什麼  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是爸爸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米內特  這很危險你稍微退後些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼行  我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.02,0:10:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是爸爸  為了女兒我可以豁出一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是爸爸  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真考慮之後得出自己的結論了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真懂事  米內特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.52,0:11:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不怪我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果米內特認真考慮過的話  我不會怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我的選擇卻不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的…選擇？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了一些事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他  還有阿薇莉爾  現在都非常痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不只要拯救米內特和米利安姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要拯救阿貝丁和阿薇莉爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救我們？天真
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要硬著來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.30,0:11:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要全部救下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,癡人說夢話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不打算當它是夢話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:12:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以為了要實現  就得先讓眼前的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打倒我嗎  雷斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  助我一臂之力吧  阿貝丁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有何能耐！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然打破了艾爾的防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿貝丁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿貝丁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雷斯塔在的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙緹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿貝丁大人  米利安姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想同歸於盡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.97,0:13:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事  米內特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米內特  我也很任性和貪心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要的東西就不擇手段去得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:14:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  不只是我  卡莉娜也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有切露西  阿尼艾絲  尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連尼娜也是  大家都是任性  貪心的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊  米內特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.93,0:14:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想和米利安姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和阿貝丁  阿薇莉爾小姐  還有米內特在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米內特也可以跟我們一起企望得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以任性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊  別自己一個人煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是覺得辛苦的話  可以向我們委託任務哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  米內特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.36,0:15:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和爸爸  和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和米利安姆一起得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米內特…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和哥哥  和大家永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米利安姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米利安姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種狀態就別走出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為哥哥你們每次都會幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒讓你感到痛苦嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身邊總有著哥哥  有著阿薇莉爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有新的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣一直支撐著我的雙手  我知道他們非常善良
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還有願意把重要的核心送給我的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有比這更幸福的日子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米利安姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔  米內特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米利安姆小姐  阿貝丁大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔  你受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  因為我控制力道正好不會造成重傷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米內特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米內特就算我不願意也要把核心送給我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我希望米利安姆能健康起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後哥哥和阿薇莉爾為了我要將米內特…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.86,0:17:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…那個…已經不想再看到米利安姆小姐受苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而Oasis的各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我們希望能聽到米利安姆小姐的真正心意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓我把我的真正心意  把我的任性傳達給各位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想死  我想和哥哥還有大家永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米利安姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米利安姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以雷斯塔先生  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  阿貝丁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.81,0:17:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現我們的任性要求吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這委託我們接下了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了  就和這工會聯手  一起尋找方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米利安姆小姐  米內特姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.30,0:18:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你擠過去也沒人會怪你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.88,0:18:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達成和解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿薇莉爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米利安姆小姐  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也該謝謝阿薇莉爾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和阿薇莉爾在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.09,0:18:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米內特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來大家都沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起讓你們擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可不是你們上演和諧一幕的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:18:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加內特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情一會再說  快回Oasis  出大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.28,0:19:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊大家一起衝回去吧  出大事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣  真是出大事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天上突然哆啪地冒出光來  叭叭地流到山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後晶石怪物嘩啦嘩啦的  太嚇人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上為調查結果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便一提報酬請用雷斯塔自身來支付
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從天上鋪下來的光之道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是從天蓋的水車向衛星的逆流的艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界末日即將降臨  哈米吉多頓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.66,0:19:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從天蓋的水車？阿貝哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:20:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是師父所在之地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.14,0:20:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能現在正發生什麼重大變故
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是安定世間艾爾的東西發生異常了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  情況非常緊迫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾爾亂流  晶石怪物暴走  數量越來越多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話不僅是埃爾塔利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個世界都會被晶石怪物襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.61,0:20:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是所謂的世界危機
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  如果米利安姆的核心異常也是天蓋的水車造成的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解決它的話  米利安姆就會好起來？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.62,0:20:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  就算沒有好起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也或許會找得到救米利安姆的線索
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.74,0:20:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  阿貝哥  阿薇莉爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:20:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那米內特在這真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魂白珠是能安定艾爾的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能在解決天蓋的水車的暴走時起作用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是稀奇啊  媽媽竟然會給我們提示
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是給認真考慮過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.82,0:21:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後回來了的米內特的獎勵哦
